description: A long counter, manned by a flour-dusted young elf, runs the length of the room, displaying the various rations for sale.  Savory smells of roasting meat, baking bread and pungent spices drift from behind a set of swinging doors in the back wall.  Occasionally, the dark, rich scent of chocolate wafts in from the kitchen, but there are no chocolates laid out on the display counter.
title: [Annatto Rations Shop]
